<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=1440">
    <title>BABATHE.COM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/babathe.css">
    <script src="../../js/library.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="layerPop open" id>
        <div class="cont w-440">
            <h1 class="layerTitle">배송지 확인</h1>
            <div class="layerBody">
                <div class="ly-addr-area">
                    <div class="recent">
                        <div class="addr-info">
                            <span class="name">김바바 (집)</span>
                            <span class="phone">010.1234.5678</span>
                            <span class="addr"><span class="zipcode">[06531]</span> 서울특별시 서초구 신반포로 339 (논현빌딩) 바바패션 6층</span>
                            <div class="btn-area">
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-tx">배송지 목록</a>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-tx">삭제</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-box">
                            <select class="placeholderOn selected" >
                                <option disabled  hidden>메시지를 입력하거나 선택해 주세요.</option>
                                <option selected>직접 입력</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-box">
                            <input type="text" value="빠른 배송 부탁드려요." placeholder="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="btn-bottom-group">
                    <button type="button" type="button" class="btn">취소</button>
                    <button type="button" type="button" class="btn primary">변경</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-close" onclick="popClose('lyMybaba')">팝업닫기</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>